# WebTestAI - Git Ignore

## Dependencies
node_modules/
package-lock.json

## Test Output (exclude all test results)
output/test-*/
output/*.html
output/*.pdf
output/reports/

## But allow test-session code
!output/test-session/hybrid-test-arch/core/
!output/test-session/hybrid-test-arch/prompts/
!output/test-session/hybrid-test-arch/skills/
!output/test-session/hybrid-test-arch/examples/
!output/test-session/hybrid-test-arch/README.md
!output/test-session/hybrid-test-arch-v3/core/
!output/test-session/hybrid-test-arch-v3/prompts/
!output/test-session/hybrid-test-arch-v3/examples/
!output/test-session/hybrid-test-arch-v3/skills/

## Session Memory
memory/
input/

## OpenClaw State
.openclaw/

## Environment Variables
.env
.env.local
*.local.json

## IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

## OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

## Temporary Files
tmp/
temp/
*.tmp

## Screenshots (optional - uncomment if needed)
# screenshots/
# *.png

## PDF Reports (optional - uncomment if needed)
# *.pdf
